title: This case could end super PACs

description:
Trump pledged to lower grocery prices, but beef prices are up 12.8% and coffee prices are up 20.9%.

Now, Zohran Mamdani is offering a radical solution.

We went out with @accordingtothekid to ask New Yorkers — including Trump voters — what they think of city-owned grocery stores.
